{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for text area spaces"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","title":"spaces","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProviderC6spaces0A8Contract016AllSpaceSemanticgH0_pvp","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaces","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/spaces","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaces","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider\/spaces"]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","abstract":[{"text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of space","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/allspacesemantictokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"}]},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider":{"title":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens of text area","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"TextAreaComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"text area"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text area"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider/spaces":{"title":"spaces","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider\/spaces","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/spaces","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for text area spaces","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaces","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}}}